{"tid":538202,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"Twice 邊個最靚同邊個最Girlfriendable","createTime":"2018-01-23T12:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T04:15:11.000Z","uid":149857,"like":13,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"75eb8425c9d1a6d4dcaf46511e2d6b391ed6e882","tid":538202,"uid":149857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[/<span style=\"color: red;\">最靚：Mina</span>size=5]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/195407_85ab677bfb0a5292880cfb90117f2d3c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F195407_85ab677bfb0a5292880cfb90117f2d3c.jpeg&h=72134882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明眼人一睇就知Mina五官一定係最精緻，不過通常咁靚嘅女仔通常性格都好閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Competition:子瑜</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/200818_dbd0079840b7e481030a7ea229258314.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F200818_dbd0079840b7e481030a7ea229258314.jpeg&h=79c944cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紙魚唔係唔靚，但係我覺得佢樣子辨認度不足，好難第一眼對佢留下深刻印象<br />\n<br />\n[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\">最Girlfriendable:</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/200233_0801ee24e62c1c52bb4b93e4fabdbc78.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F200233_0801ee24e62c1c52bb4b93e4fabdbc78.jpeg&h=66d34b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n志效個樣唔係特別靚，但係肥底好有女朋友氣質，感覺有種親和力好容相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想瘋狂後入志效 撞到卟卟聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Competition:None</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：非Kpop非Twice粉"